Package: ipsec-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: IPsec utilities
 IPsec (Internet Protocol security) offers end-to-end security for
 network traffic at the IP layer.
 .
 This package is a community-maintained continuation of the Linux port
 of the KAME IPsec utilities, with full OpenSSL 1.1.x and 3.x support.

Package: racoon
Architecture: any
Provides: ike-server
Depends: adduser,
         debconf (>= 0.2.26) | debconf-2.0,
         ipsec-tools (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${perl:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: IPsec Internet Key Exchange daemon
 IPsec (Internet Protocol security) offers end-to-end security for
 network traffic at the IP layer.
 .
 This package is a community-maintained continuation of the Linux port
 of the KAME IKE daemon (racoon), with full OpenSSL 1.1.x and 3.x
 support and continued active maintenance.
